1. Pitu si se izgubio? (*Pitu* - adverb, at the beginning of the sentence) (Did you get lost?)
2. Je l' možeš *pitu* malo brže? (*pitu* - verb, imperative mood) (Can you hurry up a bit?)
3. Ne mogu da verujem da si *pitu* tako dobar pevač! (*pitu* - adjective) (I can't believe you are such a good singer!)
4. Vidim *pitu* društvo, ali ne vidim tebe. (*pitu* - noun) (I see the company, but I don't see you.)
5. Mislim da je *pitu* ovo najbolje rešenje. (*pitu* - adverb, in the middle of the sentence) (I think this is the best solution.)